        <span>FAQ Sections</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">FAQ Sections</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted max-w-3xl">
        Frequently asked questions components with clear AI naming conventions. Perfect for addressing customer
        questions and improving support.
